Poetical metres, modes, measures, and rhythms</th></tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content">
<div class="hlist">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Shloka" title="Shloka">Salok</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Savaiya" title="Savaiya">Savaiya</a></li>
