<li id="cite_note-britggs1-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-britggs1_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-britggs1_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/Adi-Granth-Sikh-sacred-scripture">Adi Granth</a>, Encyclopaedia Britannica</span>
